reviews.review_text: Solid solid show. This is a pretty decent AUD.  Remember that this civic center was fairly vast and cavernous.  The recording cant avoid that but all in all its a good DL.  The boys are definitely on and energized.  Second set opens with 7 songs before drums.  Strong effort
Nak 700's, not nak 300's Info file has wrong mics listed.
